  <name>Nitrokey App2</name>
  <summary>Manage your Nitrokey 3 device</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
	    Nitrokey 3 is an advanced open source/open hardware USB key supporting FIDO2, an OpenPGP Card, PIV and a Password-Safe including OTPs.
      This package contains the new Nitrokey-App2, which allows accessing, updating and managing Nitrokey 3 devices.
    </p>
  </description>
